The following placement of files, event, and int value will grant the local palyer the abiliity to throw grenades from an inventory limited by the initial value of <int grenade> 
parented to grenade.lua:

StarterPlayer/StarterPlayerScripts/grenade.lua
StarterPlayer/StarterPlayerScirpts/grenade.lua/<int Grenades>
ServerStorage/GrenadeExplode.lua
ServerScriptService/GrenadeCreate.lua
ReplicatedStorage/<GrenadeEvent>
